Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.94,0:00:06.67,Default1,,0,0,0,,宁静温馨的圣诞前夜
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.71,0:00:11.66,Default1,,0,0,0,,偶然的遭遇却引发了悲剧的激斗
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.32,0:00:14.99,Default1,,0,0,0,,扑朔迷离的「真实」
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.59,0:00:16.92,Default1,,0,0,0,,笼罩夜天的暗影
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.63,0:00:18.91,Default1,,0,0,0,,被噩梦吞噬的心愿
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.89,0:00:24.64,Default1,,0,0,0,,命运之子洒下的泪水
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.87,0:00:26.76,Default1,,0,0,0,,唤醒了幽远的混沌
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.26,0:00:30.01,Default1,,0,0,0,,漫长而残酷的咒夜
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.71,0:00:33.50,Default1,,0,0,0,,静静地拉开了帷幕
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.18,0:00:37.39,Default1,,0,0,0,,魔法少女奈叶A's
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.03,0:00:39.07,Default1,,0,0,0,,要开始了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.84,0:02:38.89,Default1,,0,0,0,,快一点！ 快一点！
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.55,0:02:42.79,Default1,,0,0,0,,这里已经不行了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.07,0:02:43.84,Default1,,0,0,0,,快撤退！
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.27,0:02:49.70,Default1,,0,0,0,,这里是二号舰「艾斯提亚」
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.94,0:02:52.31,Default1,,0,0,0,,「暗之书」依然在暴走中
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.79,0:02:55.30,Default1,,0,0,0,,驱动炉与舰桥都被侵蚀
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.60,0:03:03.87,Default1,,0,0,0,,掌舵系统与「虹弓炮」也被控制…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.67,0:03:08.62,Default1,,0,0,0,,「艾斯提亚」出现「虹弓炮」装填反应
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.06,0:03:10.90,Default1,,0,0,0,,发射轨道对准了本舰队
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.84,0:03:14.96,Default1,,0,0,0,,克莱德提督 立刻撤退吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.45,0:03:17.64,Default1,,0,0,0,,废弃「艾斯提亚」
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.12,0:03:22.58,Default1,,0,0,0,,全体乘员都已安全撤退
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.79,0:03:27.85,Default1,,0,0,0,,距离「虹弓炮」装填结束\N\N仅剩下一分钟左右
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.45,0:03:30.90,Default1,,0,0,0,,我将装填计时传送给您
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.75,0:03:34.33,Default1,,0,0,0,,请在发射之前 击毁本舰
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.99,0:03:35.76,Default1,,0,0,0,,通讯中断…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.51,0:03:40.55,Default1,,0,0,0,,「艾斯提亚」距离装填结束 剩余68秒
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.88,0:03:43.00,Default1,,0,0,0,,本舰的装填已经结束
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.21,0:03:44.51,Default1,,0,0,0,,随时可以发射
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.77,0:03:45.63,Default1,,0,0,0,,父亲！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.70,0:03:49.75,Default1,,0,0,0,,「虹弓炮」 炮阵展开
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.41,0:03:52.00,Default1,,0,0,0,,在计时结束之前
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.94,0:03:55.21,Default1,,0,0,0,,击毁「艾斯提亚」
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.41,0:04:27.01,Default1,,0,0,0,,一切都是我的失误
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.01,0:04:29.59,Default1,,0,0,0,,我没有预料到
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.76,0:04:35.05,Default1,,0,0,0,,暴走的「暗之书」\N\N竟能够夺取战舰的操控权
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.01,0:04:52.02,Default1,,0,0,0,,#10 \N\N命运
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.37,0:04:56.95,Default1,,0,0,0,,目标区域的通讯妨碍消失
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.19,0:04:58.38,Default1,,0,0,0,,显示影像
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.86,0:05:01.69,Default1,,0,0,0,,克洛诺呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.81,0:05:03.41,Default1,,0,0,0,,已在赶往现场的途中
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.56,0:05:11.56,Default1,,0,0,0,,好 结界已成功展开
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.28,0:05:13.73,Default1,,0,0,0,,「罗兰圣剑」准备好了吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.00,0:05:15.06,Default1,,0,0,0,,准备好了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.26,0:05:25.08,Default1,,0,0,0,,{\t(\bord4\3c&H87A1F56&)}天魔灭迹
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.80,0:05:31.06,Default1,,0,0,0,,空间攻击！？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.12,0:05:32.97,Default1,,0,0,0,,融入暗黑的色彩吧…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.10,0:05:39.23,Faqi,,0,0,0,,{\t(\bord4\3c&H88000BB&)}Round Shield{\fs22}\N\N{\fs66}魔力环盾
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.88,0:05:54.90,Default1,,0,0,0,,她们坚持得住吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.48,0:05:58.73,Default1,,0,0,0,,希望至少坚持到暴走的瞬间
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.44,0:06:10.69,Default1,,0,0,0,,「镇魂枷锁」
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.32,0:06:14.05,Default1,,0,0,0,,在拘束的同时
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.22,0:06:16.21,Default1,,0,0,0,,解除强化魔法的效力
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.06,0:06:20.40,Default1,,0,0,0,,尽管很少有机会使用
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.90,0:06:23.52,Default1,,0,0,0,,但这种情况下会派上用场
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.00,0:06:30.71,Default1,,0,0,0,,变身魔法也会被强制解除的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.63,0:06:45.54,Default1,,0,0,0,,克洛诺 你这家伙…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.63,0:06:48.84,Default1,,0,0,0,,我可从没传授过这种魔法呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.22,0:06:52.97,Default1,,0,0,0,,是你们教诲我 要学会独自成长的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.10,0:06:56.22,Default1,,0,0,0,,艾利娅… 罗蒂…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.69,0:07:05.70,Default1,,0,0,0,,躲起来了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.24,0:07:12.34,Default1,,0,0,0,,奈叶 对不起…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.10,0:07:13.87,Default1,,0,0,0,,谢谢你
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.12,0:07:14.87,Default1,,0,0,0,,不要紧吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.24,0:07:16.99,Default1,,0,0,0,,嗯 没事的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.00,0:07:21.12,Default1,,0,0,0,,她是广域攻击型呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.62,0:07:23.38,Default1,,0,0,0,,她的攻击想必很难回避吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.25,0:07:25.01,Default1,,0,0,0,,雷光战斧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.84,0:07:26.71,Faqi,,0,0,0,,Yes sir.{\fs22}\N\N{\fs66}是 主人
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.25,0:07:29.13,Faqi,,0,0,0,,Barrier Jacket Lightning Form{\fs22}\N\N{\fs66}防护服 闪电形态
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.99,0:07:33.78,Default1,,0,0,0,,给你
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.80,0:07:37.56,Default1,,0,0,0,,疾风…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.27,0:07:46.90,Default1,,0,0,0,,奈叶
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.15,0:07:48.03,Default1,,0,0,0,,菲特
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.90,0:07:50.66,Default1,,0,0,0,,尤诺君
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.11,0:07:51.82,Default1,,0,0,0,,艾尔芙
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.66,0:07:53.44,Default1,,0,0,0,,主人啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.74,0:07:56.78,Default1,,0,0,0,,我一定会实现您的心愿
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.99,0:08:07.34,Default1,,0,0,0,,我将亲手破坏\N\N那些伤害了您心爱的守护者们的罪人
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.50,0:08:10.84,Faqi,,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,585)\t(0,1170,1,\bord4\3c&H87A1F56&)\t(1170,2340,1,\bord4\3c&HFFFFFF&)}　Gefängnis der Magie　{\fs22}\N\N{\fs66}封锁领域
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.14,0:08:21.77,Default1,,0,0,0,,这是什么…！？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.26,0:08:24.52,Default1,,0,0,0,,是与上次相同的封锁结界
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.77,0:08:28.15,Default1,,0,0,0,,她果然是在追杀我们…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.40,0:08:30.90,Default1,,0,0,0,,克洛诺正在研究解决方案
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.53,0:08:33.03,Default1,,0,0,0,,援军也在赶往这里
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.15,0:08:34.28,Default1,,0,0,0,,但需要时间
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.41,0:08:37.53,Default1,,0,0,0,,在这之前 只能靠我们几个尽力而为吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.03,0:08:38.77,Default1,,0,0,0,,嗯…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.29,0:08:43.04,Default1,,0,0,0,,奈叶…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.62,0:08:46.04,Default1,,0,0,0,,嗯 我没事的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.80,0:08:51.17,Default1,,0,0,0,,{\t(\bord4\3c&H87A1F56&)}迅风天马
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.80,0:08:52.92,Default1,,0,0,0,,展翅翱翔吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.55,0:08:55.05,Faqi,,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,450)\t(0,1050,1,\bord4\3c&H87A1F56&)\t(1050,1500,1,\3c&HFFFFFF&)}Sleipnir{\fs22}\N\N{\fs66}迅风天马
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.14,0:09:14.40,Default1,,0,0,0,,莉泽她们是遵从于您的指令吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.53,0:09:16.53,Default1,,0,0,0,,格雷姆提督
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.11,0:09:18.24,Default1,,0,0,0,,不是的 克洛诺
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.37,0:09:19.74,Default1,,0,0,0,,这是我们的独断行为
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.24,0:09:21.70,Default1,,0,0,0,,不关父亲的事
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.12,0:09:23.41,Default1,,0,0,0,,罗蒂 艾利娅
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.87,0:09:24.75,Default1,,0,0,0,,不必庇护我了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.62,0:09:28.63,Default1,,0,0,0,,克洛诺已经掌握了大致情况
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.32,0:09:30.27,Default1,,0,0,0,,对吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.80,0:09:35.67,Default1,,0,0,0,,11年前的「暗之书」事件之后
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.80,0:09:41.18,Default1,,0,0,0,,提督您独自搜寻过「暗之书」的转生目标吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.06,0:09:46.15,Default1,,0,0,0,,并且 您找到了「暗之书」的所在
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.64,0:09:49.23,Default1,,0,0,0,,以及现在的主人── 八神疾风
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.10,0:09:54.01,Default1,,0,0,0,,但是 即使捕获完成前的「暗之书」和主人
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.14,0:09:55.49,Default1,,0,0,0,,也没有多大的意义
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.24,0:09:57.74,Default1,,0,0,0,,因为无论是逮捕它的主人
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.86,0:09:59.49,Default1,,0,0,0,,还是破坏掉「暗之书」
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.37,0:10:02.24,Default1,,0,0,0,,它都会立刻转生的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.74,0:10:07.39,Default1,,0,0,0,,因此 您在监视中静候着「暗之书」的完成
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.25,0:10:14.76,Default1,,0,0,0,,您找到了永久封印「暗之书」的方法吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.13,0:10:21.21,Default1,,0,0,0,,看到那个父母双亡 身患残疾的女孩
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.14,0:10:23.60,Default1,,0,0,0,,我的内心也很痛苦
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.34,0:10:25.97,Default1,,0,0,0,,但这便是「命运」吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.12,0:10:31.81,Default1,,0,0,0,,她越是孤独 会为她难过的人也便越少
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.48,0:10:34.66,Default1,,0,0,0,,自称是她父亲的朋友
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.72,0:10:38.53,Default1,,0,0,0,,为她的生活提供资助的 也是您吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.41,0:10:44.82,Default1,,0,0,0,,在迎来永恒长眠前\N\N我希望能让她享受一丝幸福
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.51,0:10:49.58,Default1,,0,0,0,,我真是伪善啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.08,0:10:51.46,Default1,,0,0,0,,封印的方法是
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.83,0:10:54.09,Default1,,0,0,0,,将「暗之书」与主人一同冻结
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.46,0:10:57.70,Default1,,0,0,0,,禁锢于次元罅隙 或冰封世界之中
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.72,0:11:00.34,Default1,,0,0,0,,这便是您的计划吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.59,0:11:01.09,Default1,,0,0,0,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.59,0:11:06.34,Default1,,0,0,0,,这样一来 「暗之书」便不会转生
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.47,0:11:09.73,Default1,,0,0,0,,至今为止的「暗之书」之主们
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.85,0:11:11.98,Default1,,0,0,0,,也有很多人都被「虹弓炮」蒸发了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.48,0:11:14.36,Default1,,0,0,0,,这与此没有任何区别
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.48,0:11:16.76,Default1,,0,0,0,,克洛诺 现在还并不太迟
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.48,0:11:19.11,Default1,,0,0,0,,快点释放我们
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.74,0:11:21.49,Default1,,0,0,0,,实施冻结的机会
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.74,0:11:24.62,Default1,,0,0,0,,只有暴走开始瞬间的几分钟时间
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.87,0:11:26.16,Default1,,0,0,0,,但在那一刻
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.37,0:11:30.76,Default1,,0,0,0,,「暗之书」之主的罪行\N\N并不足以遭受永久冻结
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.00,0:11:32.88,Default1,,0,0,0,,这是违法的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.00,0:11:33.95,Default1,,0,0,0,,就因为这些…！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.38,0:11:35.88,Default1,,0,0,0,,就是因为这些法律
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.00,0:11:37.63,Default1,,0,0,0,,悲剧才会被一次次重演
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.01,0:11:39.26,Default1,,0,0,0,,克莱德君也是…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.13,0:11:42.01,Default1,,0,0,0,,你的父亲也因此才…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.01,0:11:42.60,Default1,,0,0,0,,罗蒂
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.34,0:11:51.49,Default1,,0,0,0,,除了法律问题外
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.35,0:11:54.95,Default1,,0,0,0,,提督的计划还存在另一个漏洞
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.46,0:11:59.80,Default1,,0,0,0,,首先 冻结的解除并非难事
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.63,0:12:02.14,Default1,,0,0,0,,无论将它藏于何处
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.19,0:12:03.49,Default1,,0,0,0,,无论如何去守护它
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.69,0:12:07.55,Default1,,0,0,0,,迟早将会有人企图利用它
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.56,0:12:09.85,Default1,,0,0,0,,愤怒与悲哀
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.10,0:12:11.44,Default1,,0,0,0,,欲望与渴求
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.47,0:12:16.80,Default1,,0,0,0,,这些心愿会诱惑人们走向禁忌的力量
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.36,0:12:21.77,Default1,,0,0,0,,我很担心现场状况
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.26,0:12:24.92,Default1,,0,0,0,,对不起 暂时失陪了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.60,0:12:27.22,Default1,,0,0,0,,克洛诺
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.22,0:12:28.72,Default1,,0,0,0,,是？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.35,0:12:31.48,Default1,,0,0,0,,艾利娅 把「罗兰圣剑」交给他
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.73,0:12:32.48,Default1,,0,0,0,,父亲…？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.60,0:12:33.60,Default1,,0,0,0,,怎么可以这样做…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.60,0:12:37.07,Default1,,0,0,0,,我们已经没有机会了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.73,0:12:39.62,Default1,,0,0,0,,拿在手里 也不会派上用场
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.32,0:12:45.02,Default1,,0,0,0,,至于如何使用 就由你来决定了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.48,0:12:50.72,Default1,,0,0,0,,这便是冰结之杖── 「罗兰圣剑」
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.28,0:13:25.20,Default1,,0,0,0,,粉碎吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.12,0:13:27.70,Faqi,,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,600)\t(0,980,1,\bord4\3c&H87A1F56&)\t(980,1580,1,\3c&HFFFFFF&)}Breakup{\fs22}\N\N{\fs66}粉碎
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.68,0:13:31.88,Faqi,,0,0,0,,{\t(\bord4\3c&H00BBBB&)}Plasma Smasher{\fs22}\N\N{\fs66}雷子震破
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.62,0:13:34.33,Default1,,0,0,0,,发射！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.21,0:13:37.27,Faqi,,0,0,0,,{\t(\bord4\3c&H88000BB&)}Divine Buster Extension{\fs22}\N\N{\fs66}天神烈破{\fnsimhei}·{\r}{\t(\bord4\3c&H88000BB&)}{\fs66}EX
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.33,0:13:39.46,Default1,,0,0,0,,发射！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.76,0:13:45.51,Default1,,0,0,0,,圣盾
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.51,0:13:47.01,Faqi,,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,450)\t(0,1050,1,\bord4\3c&H87A1F56&)\t(1050,1500,1,\3c&HFFFFFF&)}Panzerschild{\fs22}\N\N{\fs66}精钢圣盾
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.77,0:13:57.04,Default1,,0,0,0,,腥红的利刃 血光的裁决
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.25,0:13:59.51,Faqi,,0,0,0,,{\t(\bord4\3c&H87A1F56&)}Blutiger Dolch{\fs22}\N\N{\fs66}嗜血绯刃
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.11,0:14:04.78,Default1,,0,0,0,,穿噬吧 嗜血绯刃
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.20,0:14:21.42,Default1,,0,0,0,,毁灭之光 笼罩罪人吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.30,0:14:30.18,Default1,,0,0,0,,难道…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.55,0:14:31.43,Default1,,0,0,0,,那是…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.18,0:14:33.56,Default1,,0,0,0,,汇聚的群星
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.81,0:14:37.17,Default1,,0,0,0,,化作粉碎万物的光辉
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.77,0:14:40.65,Default1,,0,0,0,,星光… 聚裂…！？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.82,0:14:46.04,Default1,,0,0,0,,艾尔芙 尤诺
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.57,0:14:47.07,Default1,,0,0,0,,明白了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.32,0:14:55.08,Default1,,0,0,0,,飞驰吧 闪光
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.45,0:14:57.58,Default1,,0,0,0,,她居然会使用奈叶的魔法
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.83,0:14:59.92,Default1,,0,0,0,,奈叶曾被蒐集过一次
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.46,0:15:02.21,Default1,,0,0,0,,一定是在那时被复制的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.33,0:15:04.09,Default1,,0,0,0,,啊… 菲特？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.21,0:15:05.71,Default1,,0,0,0,,不必躲这么远吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.05,0:15:07.15,Default1,,0,0,0,,距离太近的话
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.34,0:15:09.06,Default1,,0,0,0,,防御会被轻易粉碎的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.35,0:15:10.69,Default1,,0,0,0,,必须拉开回避距离才行
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.31,0:15:25.19,Faqi,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Sir, there are noncombatants on the left at 300 yards.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.31,0:15:25.19,Faqi,,0,0,0,,{\fs66}「左侧300码处发现普通市民」
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.45,0:15:33.09,Default1,,0,0,0,,到处都没有人呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.74,0:15:35.77,Default1,,0,0,0,,大家突然就不见了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.16,0:15:39.63,Default1,,0,0,0,,周围变得这么暗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.16,0:15:41.42,Default1,,0,0,0,,那边还有东西在闪光
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.87,0:15:43.38,Default1,,0,0,0,,到底发生了什么事
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.79,0:15:44.33,Default1,,0,0,0,,嗯…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.17,0:15:46.38,Default1,,0,0,0,,我们先快点逃吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.09,0:15:48.26,Default1,,0,0,0,,逃得越远越好
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.55,0:15:49.46,Default1,,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.06,0:15:58.93,Faqi,,0,0,0,,Distance 70{\fs22}\N\N{\fs66}距离 70
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.47,0:16:01.18,Faqi,,0,0,0,,{\fs66}60
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.90,0:16:03.58,Faqi,,0,0,0,,{\fs66}50
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.32,0:16:04.17,Default1,,0,0,0,,奈叶 就在这附近
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.12,0:16:15.66,Faqi,,0,0,0,,{\fs66}20
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.12,0:16:17.87,Faqi,,0,0,0,,{\fs66}18
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.52,0:16:19.18,Default1,,0,0,0,,哎！？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.59,0:16:29.21,Default1,,0,0,0,,那个…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.21,0:16:30.09,Default1,,0,0,0,,对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.46,0:16:33.34,Default1,,0,0,0,,现在很危险 请站在原地不要动
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.84,0:16:36.09,Default1,,0,0,0,,刚才的声音是…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.72,0:16:40.72,Default1,,0,0,0,,奈叶…？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.68,0:16:42.81,Default1,,0,0,0,,菲特…？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.61,0:16:54.86,Default1,,0,0,0,,{\t(\bord4\3c&H88000BB&)}星光聚裂
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.92,0:17:10.71,Default1,,0,0,0,,菲特 快保护爱丽莎她们
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.80,0:17:11.21,Default1,,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.97,0:17:14.83,Default1,,0,0,0,,你们站在那里不要动
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.57,0:17:16.69,Faqi,,0,0,0,,{\t(\bord4\3c&H00BBBB&)}Defenser Plus{\fs22}\N\N{\fs66}强化护御
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.89,0:17:25.23,Default1,,0,0,0,,旭日之心
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.69,0:17:28.32,Faqi,,0,0,0,,{\t(\bord4\3c&H88000BB&)}\N\NWide Area Protection{\fs22}\N\N{\fs66}广域防御
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.05,0:17:44.56,Default1,,0,0,0,,奈叶
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.16,0:17:46.23,Default1,,0,0,0,,奈叶 你们没事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.68,0:17:47.40,Default1,,0,0,0,,菲特
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.02,0:17:52.07,Default1,,0,0,0,,我们没事的…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.59,0:17:56.76,Default1,,0,0,0,,但爱丽莎和铃鹿被困在了结界内部
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.68,0:17:58.47,Default1,,0,0,0,,你说什么！？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.39,0:18:01.05,Default1,,0,0,0,,艾蜜
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.51,0:18:04.14,Default1,,0,0,0,,余波稳定后 我立刻传送她们避难
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.02,0:18:06.27,Default1,,0,0,0,,再坚持一下
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.39,0:18:07.10,Default1,,0,0,0,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.90,0:18:19.45,Default1,,0,0,0,,已经没事了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.32,0:18:22.66,Default1,,0,0,0,,很快便有人送你们去安全的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.24,0:18:25.27,Default1,,0,0,0,,再坚持一下 不要乱动
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.46,0:18:29.08,Default1,,0,0,0,,那个… 奈叶… 菲特…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.12,0:18:30.43,Default1,,0,0,0,,喂… 这到底是…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.09,0:18:38.22,Default1,,0,0,0,,被她们看到了呢…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.88,0:18:39.38,Default1,,0,0,0,,嗯…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.22,0:18:41.56,Default1,,0,0,0,,尤诺君 对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.64,0:18:44.85,Default1,,0,0,0,,能代我保护她们吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.22,0:18:46.60,Default1,,0,0,0,,艾尔芙 也拜托你了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.81,0:18:47.89,Default1,,0,0,0,,可是… 菲特…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.48,0:18:49.73,Default1,,0,0,0,,我们走吧 艾尔芙
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.81,0:18:50.65,Default1,,0,0,0,,可是…！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.06,0:18:52.08,Default1,,0,0,0,,如果心存忧虑
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.48,0:18:54.34,Default1,,0,0,0,,她们也就无法全力应战
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.00,0:18:58.53,Default1,,0,0,0,,奈叶 菲特
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.90,0:19:00.11,Default1,,0,0,0,,接到来自克洛诺君的联络
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.07,0:19:05.90,Default1,,0,0,0,,他让你们劝说「暗之书」之主…\N\N让疾风投降并停止行动
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.29,0:19:08.79,Default1,,0,0,0,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.92,0:19:11.54,Default1,,0,0,0,,疾风
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.13,0:19:13.42,Default1,,0,0,0,,还有「暗之书」
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.96,0:19:15.00,Default1,,0,0,0,,请不要这样做
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.25,0:19:19.80,Default1,,0,0,0,,伤害维塔她们的 并不是我们
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.51,0:19:22.68,Default1,,0,0,0,,希格娜姆她们与我们是…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.93,0:19:24.18,Default1,,0,0,0,,我的主人…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.97,0:19:30.23,Default1,,0,0,0,,从心底希望夺走了\N\N所爱之人的这个世界…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.23,0:19:33.73,Default1,,0,0,0,,能够是一场噩梦
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.94,0:19:38.49,Default1,,0,0,0,,我则要全力实现主人的心愿
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.44,0:19:45.24,Default1,,0,0,0,,要让主人永眠于温馨的梦境中
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.33,0:19:51.08,Default1,,0,0,0,,并且 要让夺走了心爱骑士们的罪人
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.63,0:19:54.92,Default1,,0,0,0,,坠入永恒的黑暗
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.46,0:19:56.50,Default1,,0,0,0,,暗之书！！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.25,0:20:01.88,Default1,,0,0,0,,你也以这个名字来称呼我吗
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.23,0:20:18.27,Default1,,0,0,0,,这也没有关系
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.20,0:20:26.08,Default1,,0,0,0,,我只要实现主人的心愿便足够了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.66,0:20:28.79,Default1,,0,0,0,,实现主人的心愿？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.04,0:20:31.79,Default1,,0,0,0,,实现了这样的心愿
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.75,0:20:36.04,Default1,,0,0,0,,疾风真的会高兴吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.79,0:20:38.17,Default1,,0,0,0,,封闭自己的心灵
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.80,0:20:40.05,Default1,,0,0,0,,抛弃自己的意志
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.30,0:20:43.30,Default1,,0,0,0,,仅仅作为实现主人心愿的道具而存在
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.80,0:20:45.68,Default1,,0,0,0,,你真的甘愿如此吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.60,0:20:48.22,Default1,,0,0,0,,我是魔导书
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.35,0:20:50.97,Default1,,0,0,0,,只是纯粹的道具而已
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.35,0:20:54.23,Default1,,0,0,0,,可是 你不是懂得交谈吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.48,0:20:55.98,Default1,,0,0,0,,你不是拥有心灵吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.52,0:20:58.40,Default1,,0,0,0,,如果不是 那就太奇怪了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.15,0:21:01.03,Default1,,0,0,0,,假如你真的没有心灵的话
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.65,0:21:03.78,Default1,,0,0,0,,那么又为什么会哭泣呢
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.03,0:21:06.83,Default1,,0,0,0,,这泪水是主人的泪水
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.16,0:21:09.41,Default1,,0,0,0,,我是道具
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.41,0:21:13.66,Default1,,0,0,0,,不会感到什么悲哀
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.66,0:21:16.50,Default1,,0,0,0,,防护服 爆发解除
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.00,0:21:17.96,Faqi,,0,0,0,,Sonic Form{\fs22}\N\N{\fs66}超音形态
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.22,0:21:26.76,Default1,,0,0,0,,「不会感到什么悲哀」…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.57,0:21:31.49,Default1,,0,0,0,,以如此悲哀的表情说出这种话来
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.10,0:21:33.64,Default1,,0,0,0,,又有谁会相信呢
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.30,0:21:36.60,Default1,,0,0,0,,你也拥有自己的心灵
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.35,0:21:39.12,Default1,,0,0,0,,你也可以倾诉悲哀的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.94,0:21:47.48,Default1,,0,0,0,,你的主人… 善良的疾风一定会回应你的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.04,0:21:50.28,Default1,,0,0,0,,所以 快点解放疾风吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.20,0:21:52.33,Default1,,0,0,0,,解除你的武装吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.12,0:21:53.83,Default1,,0,0,0,,拜托你了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.72,0:22:10.65,Default1,,0,0,0,,真快啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.67,0:22:13.71,Default1,,0,0,0,,崩溃已经开始了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:22:14.70,0:22:17.69,Default1,,0,0,0,,我很快便会丧失自己的意志
Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.48,0:22:21.69,Default1,,0,0,0,,那样一来 很快便会陷入暴走
Dialogue: 0,0:22:22.73,0:22:24.27,Default1,,0,0,0,,在失去意识之前
Dialogue: 0,0:22:25.36,0:22:28.96,Default1,,0,0,0,,我必须实现主人的心愿
Dialogue: 0,0:22:30.27,0:22:32.12,Faqi,,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,450)\t(0,1400,1,\bord4\3c&H87A1F56&)\t(1400,1850,1,\3c&HFFFFFF&)}Blutiger Dolch{\fs22}\N\N{\fs66}嗜血绯刃
Dialogue: 0,0:22:36.37,0:22:38.62,Default1,,0,0,0,,坠入暗黑的深渊吧…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.51,0:22:48.38,Default1,,0,0,0,,你这… 任性的孩子…！！
Dialogue: 0,0:22:49.08,0:22:50.14,Faqi,,0,0,0,,{\t(\bord4\3c&H00BBBB&)}Sonic Drive{\fs22}\N\N{\fs66}超音帆羽
Dialogue: 0,0:22:52.26,0:22:53.12,Default1,,0,0,0,,为什么…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:53.56,0:22:54.50,Faqi,,0,0,0,,Ignition{\fs22}\N\N{\fs66}驱动
Dialogue: 0,0:22:55.72,0:22:56.60,Default1,,0,0,0,,如此固执！！
Dialogue: 0,0:22:59.73,0:23:04.23,Default1,,0,0,0,,你也在我之中长眠吧
Dialogue: 0,0:23:15.24,0:23:16.37,Default1,,0,0,0,,菲特！！
Dialogue: 0,0:23:21.88,0:23:23.34,Faqi,,0,0,0,,Absorption
Dialogue: 0,0:23:24.59,0:23:29.22,Default1,,0,0,0,,一切都将沉入温馨的长眠…
Dialogue: 0,0:25:09.32,0:25:12.13,Default1,,0,0,0,,菲特被封闭在了「暗之书」之中
Dialogue: 0,0:25:12.62,0:25:15.79,Default1,,0,0,0,,疾风在「暗之书」的内部沉睡着
Dialogue: 0,0:25:16.33,0:25:20.68,Default1,,0,0,0,,飘舞在圣夜天空中 那来自过去的记忆与悲哀
Dialogue: 0,0:25:20.84,0:25:23.41,Default1,,0,0,0,,以及… 一份小小的礼物
Dialogue: 0,0:25:24.16,0:25:28.47,Default1,,0,0,0,,下集 魔法少女奈叶A's 第11话
Dialogue: 0,0:25:28.90,0:25:30.32,Default1,,0,0,0,,圣夜的礼物
Dialogue: 0,0:25:30.64,0:25:33.11,Default1,,0,0,0,,心愿一定能够实现
